erfection Through Your Voice</h2>\n<p>At Noir Nail Bar, we value your feedback and continuously adapt to meet your needs. Your suggestions inspire us to improve, ensuring every visit is even better than the last.</p>\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-07 09:58:22', '2025-05-07 09:58:22', '', 2, 'http://localhost:8888/info189/?p=156', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
